:: Hack Build PoC {"position":"100,1125","size":"100,100"}
You push deeper into the exploit.  
Hours turn into a focused blur as you refine your proof of concept into a stable tool. With the right antenna configuration and timing, you can trigger an implant reset from a short distance, reliably and silently.

You stare at the tool for a moment.  
It’s more powerful than you expected.

With a vulnerability like this, you now hold several possible futures in your hands:
• You could profit by selling it to the highest bidder.  
• You could publish it and force worldwide attention overnight.  
• Or you could take responsibility and disclose it properly even if it means giving up control and recognition.

This is no longer just research. It’s a crossroads.

**What do you do next?**

• [[Sell or trade the exploit to dark-web buyers.|Hack Sell Exploit]]  
• [[Publish full technical details online or in a public talk.|Hack Public Release]]  
• [[Stop and report the vulnerability responsibly to Corazón instead.|Hack Late Disclosure]]



